      "correctIndex": 0,
      "rationale": "大人 (おとな - adult). Jukujikun (semantic compound reading): the kanji 大 and 人 are individually N5, but the compound reading おとな is irregular. The compound is documented as an N5 vocab entry in vocabulary_n5.md; the irregular-reading pattern is standard for N5 family/age vocabulary.",
      "kbSourceId": "Q55",
      "id": "moji-4.10",
      "mondai": 2,
      "rationale_hi": "大人 (おとな — वयस्क)। 熟字訓 (जुकुजिकुन, अर्थ-आधारित संयुक्त पठन): कान्जी 大 और 人 अलग-अलग N5 हैं, पर संयुक्त पठन おとな अनियमित है।",
      "rationale_hi_provenance": "native_reviewed_2026_05_18",
      "grammarPatternId": "n5-041",
      "grammarPatternId_provenance": "auto_inferred"
    },
